---

<section class="animate" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <div class="text-center mb-10">
    <h2
      id="about-heading"
      class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 via-purple-900 to-gray-900 dark:from-white dark:via-purple-300 dark:to-white bg-clip-text text-transparent">
      About Me
    </h2>
    <div
      class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 mx-auto rounded-full">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          I'm <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >Rizky Eka Haryadi</strong
          >, a dedicated
          <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >Mobile Developer</strong
          > with a strong passion for building modern, cross-platform applications
          that deliver smooth and intuitive user experiences.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          I specialize in developing apps using <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >Flutter</strong
          > and <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >React Native</strong
          >, with additional experience in <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >Kotlin</strong
          >,
          <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >Java</strong
          >, and <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >Swift</strong
          >. My focus is on writing clean, maintainable code and delivering
          polished UIs that meet real-world needs.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          I also enjoy exploring <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >backend integration</strong
          >, using tools like <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >Firebase</strong
          >, <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >Supabase</strong
          >, and <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >RESTful APIs</strong
          > to create seamless full-stack mobile solutions. My mission is to build
          impactful applications that solve real problems and make everyday life
          better through technology.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Outside of mobile development, I have a growing interest in <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >Machine Learning</strong
          >
          and how it can be integrated into mobile apps â€” such as intelligent features,
          personalization, and smart recommendations. I actively learn and experiment
          with ML tools and frameworks to explore these possibilities.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Side Content -->
    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- What I Do -->
      <div
        class="backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200/50 dark:border-gray-700/50 shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl">
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg
            class="w-6 h-6"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
          What I Do
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-sm md:text-base">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
            <span
              class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            ></span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
              >Cross-platform mobile development (Flutter & React Native)</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
            <span
              class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-emerald-500 flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            ></span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
              >Backend integration with Firebase & REST APIs</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
            <span
              class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            ></span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
              >UI/UX prototyping & performance optimization</span
            >
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-3 group">
            <span
              class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-amber-500 flex-shrink-0 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform"
            ></span>
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300"
              >Publishing to Play Store & App Store</span
            >
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Currently -->
      <div
        class="backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-gray-200/50 dark:border-gray-700/50 shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl">
        <h3
          class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg
            class="w-6 h-6 animate-pulse"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
          Currently Exploring
        </h3>
        <p
          class="text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          Advancing my skills in <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >state management</strong
          > (BLoC, Provider),
          <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >native platform integration</strong
          >, <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >mobile CI/CD</strong
          >, and experimenting with <strong
            class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-cyan-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent"
            >Machine Learning in mobile apps</strong
          >
          using tools like TensorFlow Lite and Core ML.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Quick Stats -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div
          class="backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-200/50 dark:border-gray-700/50 shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl text-center">
          <div
            class="text-3xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-2">
            3+
          </div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            Years of Mobile Dev
          </div>
        </div>
        <div
          class="backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/50 dark:bg-gray-800/50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-gray-200/50 dark:border-gray-700/50 shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-2xl text-center">
          <div
            class="text-3xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-pink-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent mb-2">
            15+
          </div>
          <div class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
            Mobile Apps Built
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .animate {
    animation: fadeInUp 0.6s ease-out;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  .prose {
    @apply text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300;
  }

  .group:hover span:first-child {
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
  }
</style>
